/\  ___\   /\  == \   /\ \   /\  ___\      /\  ___\   /\ \/\ \   /\ "-.\ \   
\ \  __\   \ \  __&lt   \ \ \  \ \ \____     \ \___  \  \ \ \_\ \  \ \ \-.  \  
 \ \_____\  \ \_\ \_\  \ \_\  \ \_____\     \/\_____\  \ \_____\  \ \_\\"\_\ 
  \/_____/   \/_/ /_/   \/_/   \/_____/      \/_____/   \/_____/   \/_/ \/_/   
                </pre>
                <div class="output-line"><a href="https://github.com/therealericsun" target="_blank">GitHub</a> | <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/eric-sun-a323461a0/" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a> | <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=lAt-xWMAAAAJ&hl=en" target="_blank">Google Scholar</a> | <a href="mailto:ericsun@seas.upenn.edu">Email</a> | <a href="/Eric_Sun_Resume.pdf" download>Resume</a></div>
                <div style="height: 15px;"></div>
                <div class="output-line intro-text">My name is Eric Sun (he/him). I'm currently pusuing a joint BA/MS in Physics and BSE in Computer Science at the University of Pennsylvania. My primary interests are in machine learning, numerical optimization, and high-performance computing. I dabble a little in web and cloud development too. Explore this website by using the terminal.</div>
                <div style="height: 15px;"></div>
                <div class="output-line">Type <span class="command">help</span> to see available commands.</div>
                <div class="output-line tab-hint">Tip: Use TAB for command autocomplete and UP/DOWN to scroll terminal history</div>
                <div class="output-line">─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="input-line">
            <span class="prompt">visitor@portfolio:~$</span>
            <input 
                type="text" 
                id="command-input" 
                autofocus 
                autocomplete="off" 
                spellcheck="false" 
            />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="copyright">
        © <span id="current-year"></span> Eric Sun
    </div>

    <script>
        import '../scripts/terminal.ts';
    </script>
</body>
</html>
